high_descs: Turn around and walk to your right to reach the fridge.
Pick up the single cookie pack from the refrigerator.
Turn your left to reach the blue diningtable in the room.
Place the cookie pack on the diningtable.
Turn back and go to the cookie on the kitchen tabletop.
Take another cookie pack from the kitchen tabletop
Walk back to the blue diningtable in the room.
Place the cookie pack on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place the two cookie pack on the DiningTable

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, turn right and go straight and then hang left towards the fridge.
Pick up the cookie from the fridge.
Turn right and head straight, turn left and go straight and then hang right towards the diningtable.
Place cookie on the diningtable.
Turn around towards the cookie.
Pick up the cookie from the fridge.
Turn around towards the diningtable.
Place cookie on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Collecting cookies from different parts of the house and arranging them on a dining table.

high_descs: Turn left, move forward, then make a right turn, and walk to the fridge.
Pick up the cookie on the bottom shelf.
Walk over to the diningtable on your left.
Put the cookie down on the diningtable across from the apple.
Turn around to face the cookie.
Pick up the cookie bag next to the sink.
Turn completely around to face the diningtable again.
Put down the cookie bag next to the diningtable bag.
anns.task_desc: Put two cookie bags on the diningtable.
